translation.Name: Belgium Note - Antwerp Civilian #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: There’s nothing left here in Antwerp. It seems like everyone has scavenged anything useful.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: I think I’m going to leave Antwerp.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: I’m leaving Antwerp because I heard about a refugee camp in West Belgium. I’ll have a better chance of survival there.
